{"tid":1254893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動迷失就要搵新方向","createTime":"2019-06-24T09:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T14:25:23.000Z","uid":53481,"like":98,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1c2d33270eea39a6bd33059f491332b3e469e3","tid":1254893,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"1. 唔好抄舊橋做返之前做過嘅嘢，例如圍立會、圍犬總、圍水務大樓等。突襲先會成功，做過一次，正虎班撚樣都識諗對策啦。<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好做一啲擾民嘅事。例如圍醫院、圍水務大樓等，會令無辜巿民受影響，不利爭取民心。<br />\n<br />\n要做嘅，就要做一啲未做過、有新意、不太擾民，又會令好多人拍手叫好嘅事。例如圍律正屍、圍CCTVB電屎城、圍禮義廉總部之類。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，行動要快，聽日好出手，多啲文宣工作call馬，民意一散就好難再上返力，而家正虎龜縮避戰嘅目標都係咁，所以唔好中計，頂都只係頂多幾日，頂到G20就得。<br />\n<br />\n認同請幫推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b924f6247a91dd6f553ec9b872befce2bdd4ba21","tid":1254893,"uid":191453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警民大和解】警方高層不代表前線 市民應支持前線警員!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251511\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1100bb6a5f439e663de71cff81018249461ff6","tid":1254893,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98d962121dc6cc08912529c2a5d7a5c81af39272","tid":1254893,"uid":185628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"圍禮義廉總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5f43fde450e14809435f500f71b9df21632b17","tid":1254893,"uid":53481,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98d962121dc6c